# Local test fixtures — not committed to git.
#
# Files in here are mesh scans that are too large to commit (e.g. the
# 67MB scanned11.stl extracted from scanned11.rar on origin/main). The
# real-scan tests in test_intent_e0.py look for files here and skip
# cleanly if they don't exist, so the suite still works in environments
# that don't have the scans locally.
#
# To populate this directory from the repo's RAR archive:
#     mkdir -p backend/tests/fixtures_local
#     git show origin/main:scanned11.rar > /tmp/scanned11.rar
#     unar -o /tmp/scanned11 /tmp/scanned11.rar
#     cp /tmp/scanned11/scanned11.stl backend/tests/fixtures_local/

*
!.gitignore
!README
